title: PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs
text: > Top News PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs FILE - On top, in this Oct. 13, 2015, file photo, New York Mets' Daniel Murphy connects for his second 2015 postseason home run, against the Los Angeles Dodgers during the fourth inning of baseball's Game 4 of the National League Division Series in New York. On bottom, also in an Oct. 13, 2015, file photo, Mets' Daniel Murphy rounds the bases after hitting the solo home run against the Dodgers during the fourth inning of baseball's Game 4 of the National League Division Series in New York. Murphy won NL Championship Series MVP on Wednesday night, Oct. 21, 2015, after homering for a postseason-record sixth straight game, leading the Mets over the Chicago Cubs 8-3 to complete a four-game sweep. (AP Photo/File)
